      <title>市场押注欧洲央行加快降息，德国收益率曲线趋于正常化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/german-bond-yield-curve-normalizes-for-first-time-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商押注欧洲央行将需要加快降息步伐，且人们越来越担心该地区经济复苏已经失去动力，德国收益率曲线的一个关键部分已经正常化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/german-bond-yield-curve-normalizes-for-first-time-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
