    <item>
      <title>欧元区私营部门因制造业衰退而再次萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/euro-zone-private-sector-back-in-contraction-on-factory-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着法国奥运经济刺激政策的结束和制造业衰退的加剧，欧元区私营部门经济出现自 3 月份以来的首次萎缩，人们担心该地区经济复苏势头已经丧失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/euro-zone-private-sector-back-in-contraction-on-factory-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者对增长前景持谨慎态度，防御性股票推动欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/european-stocks-muted-as-commerzbank-drops-on-deal-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡地区经济增长放缓迹象与全球经济复苏预期，欧洲股市在防御性股票上涨的推动下小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/european-stocks-muted-as-commerzbank-drops-on-deal-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾股市上涨，降息前景带动进入牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/philippines-stock-rebound-from-june-lows-set-for-bull-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国和东南亚国家进一步放松货币政策的前景影响，菲律宾基准股票指数收于牛市区域。]]></description>
